title: Gears Of War Unoffical Custom Map Pack 1

DOCSIN (gamertag) will host games with these maps so plz b on hte look out for him n make sure you have these maps installed :D happy gaming

Instructions:
right click and copy folder "CustomMaps" and paste in:

Where to install on Vista

C:\Users\*UserName*\Documents\My Games\Gears of War for Windows\WarGame\Published\CookedPC\maps\

-------------------------
Where to install on Xp

C:\Documents and Settings\*UserName*\My Documents\My Games\Gears of War for Windows\WarGame\Published\CookedPC\maps\

if you have a customap folder just drag the 5 folders inside into you existing cusotm map folder

Happy Gaming
